VSPHERE

setup if page 503 on step 2 go on port 5480


ESXI

if error CPU not support " allowLegacyCPU=True "


Build and Patch versions

https://kb.vmware.com/s/article/2143832

Update patch command 

esxcli software vib < update/install > --deport=<path to patch .zip file or url> 

"update" use for update in the same U
"install" use for update to new U


Certificate management

/usr/lib/vmware-vmca/bin/certificate-manager

Restart port 5480 if certificate not chained

/sbin/service vami-lighttp restart

